{{Infobox power station | name = Kysinga Power Station | name_official = ''Kysinga kraftverk'' | image =Kysinga kraftverk.JPG | location_map = Møre og Romsdal | location_map_caption = Location in [[Møre og Romsdal]] county | coordinates = {{coord|63|01|06|N|9|21|53|E|type:landmark|display=inline,title}} | location = [[Rindal]], [[Møre og Romsdal]] | country = Norway | status = O | construction_began = | commissioned = {{Start date and age|2010}} | decommissioned = | cost = | owner = Kysinga Kraft AS | operator = | psps_upper_res = | psps_upper_res_capacity= | psps_penstocks = | psps_lower_res = | psps_lower_res_capacity= | psps_hydraulic_head = 135&nbsp;m | psps_generators = | psps_pumpgenerators = | psps_pumps = | ps_units_operational = | ps_units_manu_model = | ps_units_uc = | ps_units_planned = | ps_units_cancelled = | ps_units_decommissioned= | ps_electrical_capacity = 1.25 | ps_electrical_cap_fac = 59.4%<!-- 6,500 MWh/year / ( 1.25 MW * 365 days/year * 24h/day) = 0.594 --> | ps_annual_generation = 6.5 | ps_annual_gen_year = | website = | extra = }}
The '''Kysinga Hydroelectric Power Station''' ({{lang-no|Kysinga kraftverk}}) is a [[hydroelectricity|hydroelectric]] [[power station]] in the municipality of [[Rindal]] in [[Møre og Romsdal]] [[Counties of Norway|county]], [[Norway]].<ref>Oldervik, Finn. 2007. ''Kysinga kraftverk i Rindal kommune i Møre og Romsdal fylke. Virkninger på biologisk mangfold''. Bioreg AS rapport2007: 13.</ref><ref name="Kysinga">[http://www.trollheimsporten.no/kysinga-kraft-bygger-kraftstasjon.4738093-152135.html Kysinga kraft bygger kraftstasjon. 2009. ''Trollheimsporten'' (16 June).]</ref> It is a [[Run-of-the-river hydroelectricity|run-of-river hydro power station]] utilizing a drop of {{convert|135|m|sp=us}} on a tributary of the [[Surna (Norway)|Surna River]].<ref name="Kysinga"/> Permission was granted for construction in 2009<ref name="Kysinga"/> and the plant came into operation in 2010. It is operated by Kysinga Kraft AS. It operates at an installed capacity of {{nowrap|1.25 [[Megawatt|MW]]}}, with an average annual production of about 6.5&nbsp;GWh.
